Bundled Font Licenses
=====================

This plugin bundles subsets of the following fonts as base64-encoded WOFF2
files in src/templates/brand-fonts.ts for offline rendering of the brand
templates (Apple, Notion, Lovable, Wired):

- Inter (https://rsms.me/inter/)
- Hanken Grotesk (https://hanken.co/products/hanken-grotesk)
- Playfair Display (https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Playfair+Display)
- Source Serif 4 (https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Source+Serif+4)

All four fonts are licensed under the SIL Open Font License, Version 1.1.
You may use them according to the terms of that license. The full text is
available at:

https://scripts.sil.org/OFL

The brand templates reference the visual identities of Apple, Notion,
Lovable, The Verge, Wired, Claude (Anthropic), MiniMax, xAI, and Figma.
These references are for aesthetic inspiration only; this plugin is not
affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by any of those companies.
